vote.title: Authorize the second of two, one-year renewal options to the service contract with Austin Street Center to provide access to homeless recovery services for the Office of Homeless Solutions for the period October 1, 2025 through September 30, 2026, not to exceed $575,000.00 - Financing: General Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
